### **SysBackground.enableRecaptchaSolver(autoOpen)**

**Description:**
The `SysBackground.enableRecaptchaSolver(autoOpen)` function enables the automatic solving of reCAPTCHA challenges using the `SysContent.enableSafeRecaptchaSolver` method. The `autoOpen` parameter specifies whether the reCAPTCHA anchor should automatically open or not.

**Parameters:**
- **autoOpen** (Boolean): If set to `true`, the reCAPTCHA anchor will automatically open. If set to `false`, the anchor will not be opened automatically.

**Example:**

```javascript
SysBackground.enableRecaptchaSolver(true);  // Automatically open the reCAPTCHA anchor and start solving.
```